high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white desk.

Place the watch on the desk on the right side of the lamp.
Turn around and go back to the white desk.
Pick up the watch on the bottom shelf.
Turn right and move to the white dresser.
Place the watch on the dresser in between the lamp and the cell phone.

high_descs: Walk to the waste bin to your right and then turn right again and walk to the white desk.

Turn around and walk back to the white desk.
Grab the other watch on the lowest shelf of the desk.
Walk back to the white drawers on your right.
Put the watch on top of the drawer and to the right of the other watch.
